description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced community nurse to enter into a Job Share with an existing post holder for the role of Community Nurse Team Manager within the Woodbury, Exmouth and Budleigh Community Health and Social Care Team. Working with the existing post holder you will be responsible for the leadership of the Claremont and Rolle Community Nursing Teams, Community Matrons and Admiral Nurses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a member of the Cluster Management Team you will also have an opportunity to work alongside the Community Services Manager and the leads for Community Nursing, Community Therapy, Urgent Community Response, Adult Social Care and the Community Inpatient Ward at Exmouth Community Hospital to shape the development of Community Health and Social Care in the area.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Community Nurse Team Manager is a Full time post and the Job Share is offered as a 0.5WTE, with the existing post holder making up the remaining 0.5WTE.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like to know more, or would like to have an informal discussion about the role please conatct Chris Cruise, Community Services Manager on 01395 282098/ 07792566720.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our vision is to provide safe, high quality seamless services delivered with courtesy and respect. To achieve our vision we expect all our staff to uphold our Trust values. Our Trust values are: &lt;br /&gt; Honesty, Openness &amp; Integrity&lt;br /&gt; Fairness&lt;br /&gt; Inclusion &amp; Collaboration&lt;br /&gt; Respect &amp; Dignity&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;***Preference will be given to staff with ‘Priority’ and &#39;At Risk&#39; status including NHS At Risk staff throughout Devon.***&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;DUE TO THE ANTICIPATED HIGH NUMBER OF APPLICATIONS FOR THIS POST WE RESERVE THE RIGHT TO CLOSE THE VACANCY BEFORE THE CLOSING DATE.&lt;/p&gt;
